// 3.775 — Customer-note echo on the order-confirmation email. When a customer writes a note at checkout, the receipt email now echoes it back in an amber-bordered '📝 Your note to staff' panel (between the totals + the 'What to bring' block). Plain-text version mirrors with 'Your note to staff:' indented body. Closes the last gap in the customer-note signal — queue chip + modal panel + admin flag + customer order page + receipt email all show the note. lib/order-confirmation-email.ts: notes added to OrderConfirmationArgs; XSS-safe render; safe(notes) escape; null-safe / empty-string-safe. /api/orders passes notesStr ?? null. Mirror on seattle-cannabis-web v4.545. tsc clean.
